prompt.text: This is the MASTER form. Should not be used directly.

text.en: What is the household ID?
text.so: Household ID

text.en: What is the address of the household?
text.so: Waa maxay tirsiga/ numberka Guriga

text.en: Are household members present right now?
text.so: Masuulka Jooga

text.en: Has the household provided consent for participation in the survey?
text.so: Masuulka ka qayb galaha waraysiga

text.en: How long has your family been living in Hargeisa?
text.so: Mudo inteeleeg ayuu qoyskaagu ku nool yahay hargeisa

text.en: How long has your family been living in Digaale?
text.so: Mudo inteeleeg ayuu qoyskaagu ku nool yahay Digaale?

text.en: You told us your family has been living in Hargeisa for less than five years. What was the reason your family moved to Hargeisa?
text.so: waxaad noo sheegtay in qoyskiinu ku noolaayeen hargaysay in ka yar shan sano sidaa daradeed waa maxay sababtay qoyskiinu hargaysa ugu soo wareegeen?

text.en: You told us your family has been living in Digaale for less than five years. What was the reason your family moved to Digaale?
text.so: waxaad noo sheegtay in qoyskiinu ku noolaayeen Digaale in ka yar shan sano sidaa daradeed waa maxay sababtay qoyskiinu Digaale ugu soo wareegeen?

text.en: How many separate rooms do you have in your house?
text.so: Imisa qol ayaa gurigan u samaysan yahay?

text.en: Could you list the name(s) of all household members who are currently living in this household? Also include yourself.
text.so: ma ii kala sheegi kartaa magac yada dhamaan inta qof ee qoysku ka kooban yahay adigoo magacaaga ka bilaabaya

text.en:
Household members are all those who are living at this address, and who regularly share meals together.

If you do not want to list their name, you could provide their initial or nickname.
text.so:
Waa dadka qoyska ka tirsan ee ku nool gurigan isla markaana inta badan cuntada kula wadaga guriga kula seexda.

Hadii anad doonayn in aad magacyadooda noo kala sheegto ma noo sheegi kartaa naanaystooda

text.en: Have any household members left to live somewhere outside of the household during the last six months?
text.so: Miyuu jiraa qof kale oo qoyska ka tirtan oo ka tegay isla markana ku nool meel kale lixdii bilood ee u danbeyey

text.en: household_members_migrate_out_create
text.so: household_members_migrate_out_create

text.en: Have any household members died during the last six months?
text.so: miyuu jiraa qof qoyska ka tirsan oo geeriyooday lixdii bilood ee u danbeeyey

text.en: household_members_mortality_create
text.so: household_members_mortality_create

text.en: What is the main source of drinking water for members of your household?
text.so: Xagee ayaa ay ka helaan biyaha qoyskagu?

text.en: How many days in the last seven days did your household consume
text.so:
Todobadii maalmood ee lasoo dhaafay, qoyskiina imisa
maalmood ayuu kaquuta cuntooyinkaan hoos kuxusan.

text.en:
Example: If you have eaten vegetables on 4 days, write 4.

Must be a number between 0 and 7
text.so:
Tusaale: Hadii ay quuteen khudaar afar 4 maalmood waxad qortaa 4

waa in ay jiraan tiro u dhaxaysa zero iyo seven (0 and 7)

text.en: Cereals and cereal products
text.so: Cunoyinka miraha leh sida galayda

text.en: Milk and milk products
text.so: Caano iyo wixii caana ka samaysan

text.en: Oils and fats
text.so: Dux iyo saliid

text.en: Dark green leafy vegetables
text.so: Qudaarta cagaaran

text.en: Other vegetables
text.so: Qudaarta kale kale

text.en: Fruits
text.so: Hilibka Xolaha iyo Digaaga

text.en: Meat and poultry
text.so: Qaybaha/ Waaxyaha hilibka xolaha sida kelyaha/ beerka/ wadnaha

text.en: Organ meat
text.so: Beed

text.en: Eggs
text.so: Kalun

text.en: Fish
text.so: midhaha dahaadka leh sida lawska iyo harakoga, digirta ama atarka

text.en: Legumes, nuts and seeds
text.so:
Xidiidleyda, miraha dambalma sida digirta, loyska iyo miraha
kale

text.en: White roots and tubers such as potatoes, sweet potatoes, or yam
text.so: Qudaarta Carada hoosteeda laga soo guro sida baradhada iyo  Dabacase

text.en: Sweets, sugar, or sugar products
text.so: Mac macaanka, sonkorta iyo kuwa sokorta laga sameeyo

text.en: Coffee, tea, and spices
text.so: Bun,shaah iyo dirta kale ee lagu daro cabitaanka

text.en: Do you own soap?
text.so: ma haysataa saabuun

text.en: Do you own hand sanitizer?
text.so: Ma haysataa jeermis dilaha gacmaha mariyo ama lagu maydho

text.en: Is there water leakage from the walls or roof when it rains?
text.so: Ma kugu darooraa gurigaagu?

text.en: Is there a draught inside the house?
text.so: Gurigu ma leeyahay dayr ama space gudaha ah si ay hawo u soo gasho?

text.en: What are the things used inside the house for cooking?
text.so: Maxaad u isticmaashaa cunto karsashada?

text.en: Do you cook inside or outside the house?
text.so: Ma guriga gudihiisa ayaad wax ku karisaa mise dibadiia

text.en: Is ventilation such as a window present in the cooking room?
text.so: Naqas saarto ma leeyahay qolka sida daaqad marawaxad dibada naqaska u tuurta

text.en: Where are infants usually when cooking is done
text.so: Halkee lagu hayaa caruurta mujada ah, xiliga aad wax karinayso

text.en: What fuel is used to heat or light the house?
text.so: maxa loo isticmaalaa marka guriga la diirinayo ama dhaxanta laga kicinayo ama loo isticmaala iftiinsiga

text.en: Please select which of the following substances is used by at least one member of your household
text.so: Ma jiraa qof qoyska ka tirsan oo leh balwadahan hoos ku xusan?

text.en: You mentioned at least one member of your household uses tobacco. Is tobacco smoked inside your house?
text.so: Qofka aad noo sheegtay inuu tubaakada isticmaalo ma guriga ayuu ku dhex cabaa

text.en: Scan the barcode
text.so: Scan the barcode

text.en: Could you share a phone number with which we can contact you?
text.so: manala wadaagi kartaa number telephon oo laga soo waco hadii loo baahdo

text.en: We would like to ask additional questions to the following individual(s), and take a nasopharyngeal swab sample. Do you/do these individuals consent to participate in the next stage of the survey?
text.so: Waxan doonayaa in aan ku waydiiyo xog dheeri ah, sankana dheecaan lasoo shay baadho kaa qaado, markaa diyaar ma u tahay in aad nagala qayb qaadato xog ururintaa

text.en: Please upload consent image
text.so: fadlan ka qaad sawir warqada ogolaanshaha

text.en: The children below have been identified as all children aged < 5 years. Complete vaccine registration form for each child.
text.so: The children below have been identified as all children aged < 5 years. Complete vaccine registration form for each child.

text.en: Are there any other children aged <5 years who live in your household, but are not listed here?
text.so: Miyey jiraan caruur kale oo ka yar shan sano oo aan la qorin?

text.en: Ask a neighbour whether the shelter has been occupied in the last two weeks
text.so: Waydii jaar ka in gurigan la deganaa laba dii usbuuuc/todobaad ee u danbeeyey

text.en: Any comments about this address (optional)?
text.so: Any comments about this address (optional)?

text.en: The children below have been registered for vaccination. Complete vaccination form for each child.
text.so: The children below have been registered for vaccination. Complete vaccination form for each child.

text.en: Write on the consent form: household ID {{data.household_id}}
text.so: waxaad ku qortaa xaashida ogolaanshaha: tirsiga guriga {{data.household_id}}

text.en: Schedule a return appointment?
text.so: Schedule a return appointment?

text.en: When shall we return?
text.so: When shall we return?
